            "answer_text": "Same thing you do when reading, but make it in reverse form, for writing. AND STICK CLOSELY TO THE AUTHOR'S ORIGINAL INTENT/MEANINGS:  -have a good/clear intro with a key sentence outright,  -then the next paragraphs are for key details/supporting ideas;  -and a conclusion/recommendation for the ending. ",
